{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_07_03",
  "title": "天動瑠依 3話 空だけを見上げて",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "……あ。おはようございます、{user}さん\n今、少しお時間いいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah. Good morning‚ {user}-san.\nDo you have a moment?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2707405362,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、瑠依。オフは昨日までだったな\nでも、レッスンの予定時間より少し早いような……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Rui. Your day off was until yesterday‚\nBut you’re here a bit earlier than your scheduled lesson time…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ちょっと早めに来ました\n{user}さんに渡したいものがあって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I came a little early.\nI have something I wanted to give you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "これ、よろしければ\n先日のお土産です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here‚ if you don’t mind.\nIt’s a souvenir from the other day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "名物の和菓子が美味しかったので、買ってきました\nお口に合えばいいんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I bought some of the famous wagashi since they were delicious.\nI hope you like them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、わざわざありがとう。いただくよ\nその様子だと、オフは楽しめたみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ thanks for going out of your way. I’ll take them.\nJudging by your expression‚ it seems like you enjoyed your day off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\nおかげさまで、とてもリフレッシュ出来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!\nThanks to you‚ I was able to refresh myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "本当に素敵な旅館だったんです\n風情があって、部屋からの景色も良くて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was a really lovely ryokan.\nIt had a lot of atmosphere‚ and the view from our room was beautiful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6349431931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "自然の音を聞きながら、ゆったりとくつろぐ……\nあんなに落ち着いた時間は、久しぶりでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Relaxing while listening to the sounds of nature…\nIt was the first time in a while that I had such a peaceful time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それは良かった\nそういえばあの旅館、料理も美味しいって話だったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s good.\nSpeaking of which‚ I heard the food at that ryokan is delicious‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですよ！\nお膳だと思ってたら、お鍋が出てきてビックリしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It is!\nI was surprised when they brought out nabe instead of traditional meal set.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "旬の山菜や山芋を使ったお鍋だったんですけど\n味が染みててホクホクで、凄く美味しかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was a nabe with seasonal wild veggies and Japanese mountain yam.\nIt was really delicious‚ soft and flavorful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "優から聞きましたけど、{user}さんが\n予約時に頼んでくれたんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard from Yu that {user}-san\nRequested it when you made the reservation?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1088225153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。選べるって言われたからな\nトリエルならこれだろう、って思ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. They said we could choose.\nI thought‚ “This is the one for TRINITYAiLE.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、さすがですね。私達としては大満足でした\nありがとうございました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ as expected. We were very satisfied.\nThank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうだ！　温泉も凄く良かったんですよ\n特に、露天風呂が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ right! The hot spring was wonderful too.\nEspecially the open-air bath.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "泊まった当日の夕方にも入ったんですけど\n朝風呂も気持ちいいって仲居さんに勧められて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We went in the evening we arrived‚\nBut the host recommended we try it in the morning‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.2927223245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに朝は空気が冷たかったんですけど\nお湯に浸かった瞬間、本当に気持ち良くて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was definitely cold in the morning‚\nBut the moment I got in the water‚ it felt so good…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.745216636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、朝の露天風呂は一気に目が覚めるし\n気持ちいいよなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true‚ a morning open-air bath wakes you right up‚\nAnd it feels great…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "はい。立ち上る湯気がキラキラしてて\n夕方のお風呂とはまた違った趣がありましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. The rising steam was sparkling‚\nIt had a different charm from the evening bath.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "時間帯が違うだけで、景色も音も\n空気の香りすらも違うんだなって思いました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just because the time of day is different‚ the scenery‚ the sounds‚\nEven the scent of the air is different.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "思い返せば私、朝の露天風呂ってあれが初めてで\nいい体験が出来たなって思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ that was my first time in a open-air bath in the morning‚\nSo I think it was a good experience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.8472756849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。めずらしく瑠依が饒舌になるほどだから\n本当に満喫出来たんだろうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. You’re rarely this talkative‚ Rui‚ so\nYou must have really enjoyed yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "あ……\nそ、そう……かもしれません……けど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…\nTh-that… might be true… but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "うう……ちょっとはしゃぎ過ぎたかも\n忘れて下さい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… Maybe I got a little too carried away.\nPlease forget it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも！\nただリフレッシュしただけじゃありませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but!\nIt wasn’t just about refreshing ourselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui021.m4a",
      "text": "優やすみれとも、今後の目標を改めて確認出来た\n有意義な時間になりましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was a meaningful time because Yu‚ Sumire‚ and I\nwere able to reaffirm our goals for the future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.0366916383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今後の目標か……\n俺にも聞かせてくれるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Goals for the future‚ huh…\nCan you tell me about them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui022.m4a",
      "text": "もう、逃げ腰にはなりません\n変に守りの姿勢を取ったりもしません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not going to shy away anymore.\nI won’t be timid anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui023.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリでサニピに負けて\nI-UNITYでどん底を味わって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After losing to Sunny Peace at the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix‚\nAnd hitting rock bottom at I-UNITY…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui024.m4a",
      "text": "それ以来、いかに自分達が挑戦を恐れていたのか\n今回の件で痛感しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I realized how much we’ve been\nafraid of challenges this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui025.m4a",
      "text": "言葉では常に上を向いていたつもりだったのに\n心のどこかで、ずっと逃げていたんだなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought we were always looking ahead‚\nBut somewhere in my heart‚ I was running away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依達の気持ちを考えれば、仕方ないことだったと思う\n……けど確かに、臆病になっていたかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it was understandable‚ given how you were feeling‚ Rui.\n…But yeah‚ you might’ve gotten a little timid.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui026.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そんなのはやっぱり、私達らしくない\nファンのみんなも、こんな私達を望んではいない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that’s… not like us.\nOur fans don’t want to see us like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui027.m4a",
      "text": "なら、私達はこれから\n常に挑戦者であるべきだって思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So we decided that from now on‚\nWe should always be challengers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui028.m4a",
      "text": "上を目指すって、そういうことじゃないですか\nだって上には、常に強者が待ち構えてるんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s what it means to aim for the top‚ isn’t it?\nBecause there are always strong opponents waiting at the top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.7051157634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。トリエルは確かに、アイドルとして圧倒的強者だ\nでも最強ではないことも、紛うことなき事実だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. TRINITYAiLE is definitely a powerful force as idols.\nBut it’s also an undeniable fact that you’re not the strongest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 249.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui029.m4a",
      "text": "はい。でも目指すべきは、その最強とも言えるトップ\n誰も届かない高さまで、翔ぶことだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. But we’re aiming to be at the very top‚ where no one can reach…\nTo soar to heights that no one else can reach…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui030.m4a",
      "text": "地面を確認して安心を覚えるのは、もうやめます\nこれからは、遙かな高い空だけを見上げていく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m done reassuring myself by checking the ground.\nFrom now on‚ I’m going to look only at the distant‚ high sky.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 267.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui031.m4a",
      "text": "おぼつかない足下が怖くなることもあるかもしれない\nでも……大丈夫です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There may be times when I’m afraid of my unsteady footing‚\nBut… it’ll be okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui032.m4a",
      "text": "優やすみれに、星見プロのみんな\n橋本さんや三枝さん、そして父……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu and Sumire‚ everyone at Hoshimi Production‚\nHashimoto-san and Saegusa-san‚ and my father…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 284.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui033.m4a",
      "text": "何より{user}さんが、側にいる\nこれほど心強いことはありませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And above all‚ you‚ {user}-san‚ are by my side.\nThere’s nothing more reassuring than that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 293.3333536784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（……ひと皮どころか、何枚もむけて成長したな）\n（それほど、覚悟の決まった目をしている）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…She’s grown so much‚ not just one layer‚ but several.）\n（Her eyes are filled with that much determination.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 300.7666870117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "その気持ちがあれば、もう大丈夫だな\n一緒に目指していこう、アイドルの頂点を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With that feeling‚ you’ll be fine.\nLet’s aim for it together‚ the peak of idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 307.800020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui034.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　改めて{user}さん……\nこれからも、よろしくお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Once again‚ {user}-san…\nFrom now on‚ I’m in your care!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 315.3333536784,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}